{"_id":"0f9ca646-b737-4f67-b71a-7409152d9453","type":"ability","name":"Personal Stash","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/alchemy.svg","system":{"skill":"Alchemy","name":"Personal Stash","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"Increases the total number of crafted alchemical items you can safely carry by 1, and the number of Alchemy Supplies you can carry by 2.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"alchemy"}}
{"_id":"6a4ec4f3-fca2-49ed-ab0c-a4b0ecfafb19","type":"skill","name":"Alchemy","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/alchemy.svg","system":{"skill_id":"alchemy","domain":"Technology and Sciences","rank":1,"stat":"intelligence","description":"The Alchemy skill can be used to identify and create alchemical substances, as well as to safely use drugs, explosives, and poisons. Attack rolls with explosives or inhaled drugs are made with the Alchemy skill.\nYou may use your Alchemy skill to craft your own poisons, drugs, and explosives with rank less than or equal to your skill ranks using Alchemical Supplies. This takes one hour per item created. Alchemy Supplies can be purchased in most settlements with a price of 1, or you can spend an hour searching in areas of wilderness to find a number equal to half the result of the check. You may safely carry Alchemy Supplies equal to double your Alchemy ranks. \nAlchemical creations tend to be dangerous and fragile. The items you create yourself must be well-cared for, and you may only carry a number equal to your skill ranks; they can also only be safely used by someone with sufficent ranks. When you purchase alchemical items from a store, they are stable and made to be administered or used by anyone and do not count toward your maximum."}}
{"_id":"7288d16d-d592-47ac-9f06-c8a49a2bc11d","type":"ability","name":"Cocktail","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/alchemy.svg","system":{"skill":"Alchemy","name":"Cocktail","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"When creating an alchemical item, you can add the effect of one other item with a lower rating to it. These items do not have to be of the same category; a grenade may be altered to apply the effects of a poison or a poison may be altered to add the effects of a drug, for example. The effects are defended against separately.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"alchemy"}}
{"_id":"9078a8ad-8886-43b6-9413-cbb125006de8","type":"ability","name":"Explosive Trap","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/alchemy.svg","system":{"skill":"Alchemy","name":"Explosive Trap","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"You can rig an explosive to explode when a creature enters its area. You may only have one explosive rigged in this fashion at once. You can enter the area without triggering the detonation.","roll_type":"none","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"alchemy"}}
